World of Warcraft Lua Unlocker - 3.3.5a Edition

This program will unlock all of World of Warcraft's Lua functions for WoW 3.3.5a. It must be built as a DLL and then injected into World of Warcraft.

It uses pattern scanning to find and patch the insecure function check, allowing protected functions like CastSpellByName and CastSpellByID to be called from addon code.

The patch works by replacing the conditional jump (74 10) with an unconditional short jump (EB 10) to bypass the taint/security roadblock that prevents addon code from calling protected Lua functions.

Version History:
- 3.3.5a: Updated pattern bytes and offsets for WoW 3.3.5a client
- Original: Supported WoW 4.0.6a and later

Credit to _Mike for the Lua unlock method, as it is similar to the method he posted here: http://www.ownedcore.com/forums/world-of-warcraft/world-of-warcraft-bots-programs/wow-memory-editing/322192[...]

This uses the same Lua unlock method as OHack, so if OHack's Lua unlock method becomes detected then this will too!
